"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-31-Chinese-mainland-Olympians-pay-three-day-visit-to-Hong-Kong-1ww2D3PJcf6-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  A delegation of Chinese mainland athletes from the recently concluded Olympics pays a three-day visit to Hong Kong. A series of events have been held, including showcasing the athletes' skills at two demonstrations at Queen Elizabeth Stadium and Victoria Park swimming pool on August 30. CGTN reporter Laura Westbrook has the Hong Kong public's reaction to the delegation's visit.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"